text: Matveyevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Matveyevsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 106 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 9 km from Kushnarenkovo, 6 km from Starobaskakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Matveyevo
